$('#search-btn').on('click', function() {
    var val = $('#search-input').val().trim();
    if (!val) return;

    // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô lat,lon ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà
    var latlon = val.split(',');
    if (latlon.length === 2 && !isNaN(parseFloat(latlon[0])) && !isNaN(parseFloat(latlon[1]))) {
        var lat = parseFloat(latlon[0]);
        var lon = parseFloat(latlon[1]);
        showLocation(lat, lon, "‡∏ï‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πà‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏≤");
    } else {
        // ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢ Nominatim
        $.get('https://nominatim.openstreetmap.org/search', {
            q: val,
            format: 'json',
            limit: 1
        }, function(data) {
            if (data && data.length > 0) {
                var lat = parseFloat(data[0].lat);
                var lon = parseFloat(data[0].lon);
                showLocation(lat, lon, data[0].display_name);
            } else {
                alert('‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏û‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà');
            }
        });
    }
});

function showLocation(lat, lon, label) {
    if (searchMarker) {
        map_9762a9bad6ae32c1e3653a1fa9719ad2.removeLayer(searchMarker);
    }
    searchMarker = L.marker([lat, lon]).addTo(map_9762a9bad6ae32c1e3653a1fa9719ad2)
        .bindPopup(label).openPopup();
    map_9762a9bad6ae32c1e3653a1fa9719ad2.setView([lat, lon], 15);
}
